Dazzie Dee bụ onye American West Coast hip hop rapper na onye na-emepụta ihe ndekọ nke na-arụkọ ọrụ ma soro ndị na-ese ihe dịka Suga Free, Mausberg, DJ Quik, Ice Cube, Shade Sheist, K-Dee, Kool G Rap, Coolio, Mixmaster Spade, Yo-Yo, Da Lench Mob, na ụfọdụ ndị ọzọ. O wepụtara abọm abụọ naanị ya n'afọ 1996, Where's My Receipt? na The Re-Birth, ya na egwu ndị a ma ama "Knee Deep", "Everybody Wants To Be A Gangsta", na "Where You From?".
A mụrụ Lidell Williams n'ubochí irí atọ n'ọnwa Nọvemba, Los Angeles, California
Ọ gara ma gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Washington Preparatory High School n'afọ 1989
Ógè ọ dị afọ iri na anọ, Williams zutere Dr
Ọ bụ onye otu ndị otu 107th Street UG / BC Crips set, dị ka Sheppard, onye otu Skool Boyz si kwuo. Ọ bụ Dr
Dre na Sir Jinx mepụtara EP mbụ ya Turn It Loose
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị izizi so na ndekọ Lench Mob, nke Ice Cube guzobere
N'ihi ọdịiche nka, ọ hapụrụ labelụ ahụ iji dekọọ abọm mbụ ya bụ Where's My Receipt wepụtara na Capitol Records na 1995

Mgbe ahụ, o mere mbipụta ọzọ maka abọm ahụ dị ka The Re-Birth na Raging Bull Records na 1996. Ọ bụ DJ Battlecat mepụtara ya ma nwee ndị ọbịa si Ice Cube, Coolio, K-Dee na Tha Chill si Compton's Most Wanted Ọtụtụ ndị na-ewere ya dị ka West Coast classic.

Dazzie Dee (nke a maara dị ka Big "Saccs"), bụ onye na-eti egwu G-funk na onye izizi bụbu onye otu egwu West Coast Lench Mob tinyere Ice Cube, K-Dee, J-Dee, Yo-Yo, Chilly Chill, T-Bone, Shorty na ndị ọzọ. Maka ọdịiche nka, ọ hapụrụ labelụ ahụ iji dekọọ abọm izizi ya bụ Where's My Receipt wepụtara na Capitol Records na 1995. Mgbe ahụ, o mere mbipụta ọzọ maka abọm ahụ dị ka The Re-Birth na Raging Bull Records na 1996.
The Killafornia Organization bụ otu egwu Hip hop nke gụnyere South Central Cartel, Compton's Most Wanted, Bonaphyde, Dazzie Dee, Killa, Tray Deee, Hard Times & Wize Guyz
Abọm mbụ ha, Killafornia Organization, bụ nke Killa Cali Records, Thug Records wepụtara n'afọ 1996 ma mepụta ya site na 3 Strikes Prod
